claim.claim-text:
An ultraviolet-erasable nonvolatile semiconductor device, comprising:
a semiconductor substrate;
an ultraviolet-erasable nonvolatile semiconductor storage element formed in a surface of the semiconductor substrate;
a top metal formed on the semiconductor substrate; and
a protective film formed on the ultraviolet-erasable nonvolatile semiconductor storage element and the top metal, the protective film comprising a silicon nitride film and a silicon oxynitride film laminated thereon.
